Key Match Events: England collapsed from 202-2 to 309 all out
Travis Head took career-best ODI figures of four for 28
Matthew Short scored 50 from just 30 balls
Miscellaneous Highlights: Rain interrupted play, reducing the game to 20 overs per side
Others: England had never come back from 2-0 down in an ODI series to win 3-2
Adil Rashid's 35-ball 36 was his highest ODI score for seven years
